STATE EX REL. JOHNSON
v.
WHITNEY. 2018-0049 Supreme Court of Ohio. April 25, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, French, Fischer, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Prohibition. On respondents' motions to dismiss. Motions granted. Cause dismissed. On respondent's motion to restrict public access to Exhibit C of relator's second complaint. Motion granted.

Kennedy, J., dissents in part and would deny respondent's motion to restrict public access.
